title: Die Teddy Teclebrhan Show
overview: In his new variety show, Teddy packs the best of his world. The 6 new episodes contain: Love, music, comedy, celebrity guests and lots of creative chaos. Framed in a great studio show with audience and live band! The best thing: Antoine, Ernst Riedler and Percy have their very own idea of how a show like this works best - even if they are all played by Teddy...
